## ğŸ—„ï¸ SQLite Signal Schema

```sql
CREATE TABLE signals (
    timestamp TEXT,
    asset TEXT,
    price REAL,
    z_score REAL,
    signal TEXT,
    confidence REAL,
    strategy TEXT
);
```

